item.title: Hey whats the latest code for 'the perfect compiler'? v8 or v9
item.dc:creator: @x0_0wn x0 0wn
item.description:
@x0_0wn wrote:

Umm this is mine, it’s good as well as Mod Taharoks. [code]@echo off
COLOR 4
TITLE Menu

:menu
CLS
ECHO Server menu
ECHO The ULTIMATE MENU by 0wn
ECHO.
ECHO Type 1 to Compile and run.
ECHO Type 2 to Run your server.
ECHO Type 3 to Compile your server.
ECHO Type 4 to To Exit this compiler.
SET option=
ECHO.
SET /p option=Your Choice?
if %option%==1 goto compileandrunserver
if %option%==2 goto runserver
if %option%==3 goto compileserver
if %option%==4 exit
:compileandrunserver
CLS
title 0wn-Scape is compiling…
echo Compiling 0wn-Scape…
echo ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
“C:\Program Files\Java\jdk1.6.0\bin\javac.exe” -cp . *.java
title Started MF-PARADISE…
echo ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
echo Compiling 0wn-Scape. Complete…
echo ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
echo Loading 0wn-Scape. Complete…
echo ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
echo 0wn-Scape is fully compiled and loaded!
echo ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
java -Xmx1024m -cp .;./jython.jar;./MySql/mysql-connector-java-3.0.17-ga-bin.jar server
CLS
exit

:runserver
CLS
TITLE Started 0wn-Scape
ECHO 0wn-Scape is being started…
ECHO ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
java -Xmx1024m -cp .;./jython.jar;./MySql/mysql-connector-java-3.0.17-ga-bin.jar server
CLS

:compileserver
CLS
title 0wn-Scape compiling…
echo Compiling 0wn-Scape…
echo ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
“C:\Program Files\Java\jdk1.6.0\bin\javac.exe” -cp . *.java
echo Compiling complete…
echo ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
echo.
echo.
echo Type 1 to run the server!
echo Type 2 to go to the menu!
echo Type 3 to exit!
echo.
SET optioncompile=
SET /p optioncompile=What do you want to do now?
if %optioncompile%==1 goto runserver
if %optioncompile%==2 goto menu
if %optioncompile%==3 exit[/code]
